Posted on September 27, 2018

Recently I watched television and I stumbled across some sport report. Nothing special. It was about football and to be precise about the UEFA Nations League”. In short terms there exists four leagues(A, B, C, D) with three or four groupsconsisting of national teams. A is the highest ranked league and D the lowest. Each team in a group competes against each other for two times(First and second leg). The goal is to rise up to the highest league A. A game plane of all
